title: 'Long-lasting but not easy to apply'
body: It's long lasting doesn't irritate the eyes . It's easy to apply with the brush (gives you precision in easy areas not in folds esp for hooded eyes). Good control on application.Gives a good jet black colour. Economical. It might be small but it would go a long way. The formula is a bit thick so it's difficult to get a straight line in the fold and the pigment doesn't glide easily in difficult areas of hooded eyes. But u can solve this problem by dipping the brush lightly in oil. Does the trick. A good product can be used to tightline upper&lower eyelid ,add eyeliner wings and helps in doing the eyebrows as well.  Worth the money
